No. 598,

Misc., October Term, 1964.

Williamson et al. v. Gilmer et al.,

379 U. S. 955. Motion to recall and amend order of this Court of January 18, 1965, denied.

The Chief Justice, Mr. Justice Marshall, and Mr. Justice Blackmun took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.
